the requests @code{chop} to remove the final newline of a diversion, and
@code{unformat} to make the horizontal spaces adjustable again.

@Example
.box xxx
a funny
.br
test
.br
.box
.chop xxx
.unformat xxx
This is \*[xxx].
    @result{} This is a funny test.
@endExample

@xref{Gtroff Internals}.
